org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer

Class IndentedImageVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer.ImageVisitor
      • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer.TextWriterImageVisitor
        • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer.IndentedImageVisitor

  •  class IndentedImageVisitor
extends TextWriterImageVisitor
    IndentedImageVisitor walks over an FSImage and displays its structure using indenting to organize sections within the image file.
